name: Kiss, Date, Eliminate
overview: They say it only takes seven seconds for someone to make a first impression, and only 7% of a first impression is based on the words one says. "Kiss, Date, Eliminate" is a modern take on a classic party game that's taking it one step further- a dating game show.
